This product includes model weights derived from SikuRoBERTa
(SIKU-BERT/sikuroberta), created by the SIKU-BERT team,
Nanjing Agricultural University, and licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0.
Source: https://huggingface.co/SIKU-BERT/sikuroberta

Modifications:
A 3-class token-classification head (O / B-LOC / I-LOC) was added on top
of the SikuRoBERTa encoder and fine-tuned for place-name named entity
recognition on the indexed XML historical corpora of the Korean History
Database, National Institute of Korean History (국사편찬위원회).

